  <brief_title>Measuring Head Control Change With 2D Video Analysis After Utilization of Headpod in Children With Poor Head Control</brief_title>
  <acronym>headpod</acronym>
  <official_title>Measuring Head Control Changes With 2d Video Analysis After Utilization of the Headpod in Children With Cerebral Palsy and Poor Head Control</official_title>
  <sponsors>
